Package de.hu.gralog.algorithm.result

This package defines all classes needed by GrALoG-Algorithms to return an AlgorithmResult.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
AlgorithmResultListener This interface defines a listener that listens to AlgorithmResults.
DisplaySubgraphListener This interface defines a listener that is informed of changes in DisplaySubgraph.
DisplaySubgraphModeListener This interface allows listeners to listen to DisplaySubgraphMode-changes.
ElementTipsDisplayModeListener This interface allows GrALoG to listen to changes of element-tips.
ElementTipsListener This interface allows GrALoG to listen to changes of element-tips.
 

Class Summary
AlgorithmResult This class basically serves as a container for AlgorithmResultContent's.
AlgorithmResultContent The class represents a content which is displayed as part of an AlgorithmResult.
AlgorithmResultContent.SubgraphInfo<V,E> This class represents a subgraph by its edges and vertices.
AlgorithmResultContentTreeNode This class extends AlgorithmResultContent in order to form a tree of contents.
AlgorithmResultInteractiveContent This class extends AlgorithmResultContent in order to add interactivity to AlgorithmResultContents.
DisplaySubgraph This class is used by GrALoG to display subgraphs of a GrALoG-structure.
DisplaySubgraph.DisplayMode  
DisplaySubgraphMode This class represents a display-mode for subgraphs.
DisplaySubgraphMode.DisplayModeUndoableEdit  
ElementTips This class represents an element-tip that can be displayed by GrALoG.
ElementTipsDisplayMode This class represents a display-mode for element-tips.
 

Package de.hu.gralog.algorithm.result Description

This package defines all classes needed by GrALoG-Algorithms to return an AlgorithmResult. Please refer to the documentation of AlgorithmResult for further information.
